title: Janteyl Danielle Johnson
description:
Janteyl was 15 and pregnant when she disappeared from her home in Newark, Delaware on February 3, 2010.  Did she run away?  Did someone have a motive to make her vanish?  I interviewed Claudia Rivero who covered Janteyl's disappearance for NBC10 back in 2010.  She is currently making a documentary called "Where is Janteyl?"  You can find more information at whereisjanteyl.com.
